\sum\limits_{k=0}^{\infty}\frac{k}{3^k}
x=1/3
\displaystyle\sum_{k=0}^\infty x\cdot \frac{d}{dx} x^k
 \frac{k}{3^k} = kx^k = x\cdot kx^{k-1} = x\cdot \frac{d}{dx} x^k 
 \sum_{k=0}^\infty \frac{k}{3^k} = \sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{k}{3^k} = \left\{\begin{array}{cccccccccccccccc}  & & 1/3 \\ & + & 1/9 & + & 1/9 \\ & + & 1/27 & + & 1/27 & + & 1/27 \\ & + & 1/81 & + & 1/81 & + & 1/81 & + & 1/81 \\ & + & \cdots \end{array}\right. 
r=\frac{1}{3}
\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}{kr^k}=\frac{r}{(r-1)^2}
